                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090412-133-defend1124 t18090412-133-punish813"></join>
               Fined One Shilling
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
